  "extras": {
    "summary": "A JOINT RESOLUTION TO AMEND JOINT RESOLUTION NO. 202, 2025 REGULAR SESSION, TO PROVIDE THAT IN THE EVENT THE UNITED STATES SUPREME COURT ISSUES A FINAL DECISION IN THE LOUISIANA CONGRESSIONAL REDISTRICTING PLAN HOLDING THAT THE PLAN VIOLATES THE U.S. CONSTITUTION OR IS NONJUSTICIABLE, THEN THE SENATE LEGISLATIVE DISTRICTS AS PRESENTLY SET OUT SHALL BE SUPERSEDED BY JOINT RESOLUTION NO. 202, 2022 REGULAR SESSION; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
